data.description: Welcome to 3125 Croton Ave, Deltona, Florida 32738! This delightful property features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths within its 1231 sqft, offering a comfortable and spacious living environment.    Upon entering, you'll be welcomed by an open concept layout that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The high ceilings add a sense of openness and light, creating an inviting atmosphere throughout the home.    The kitchen is designed for both functionality and convenience, making it a practical space for your daily activities. As you explore the rest of the house, you'll discover the charm and comfort that each room has to offer.    Step outside to the generously sized back yard, providing a private retreat for relaxation or outdoor activities. Whether you're looking for a quiet escape or a place to entertain friends and family, this outdoor space offers versatility and tranquility.    Situated in Deltona, Florida, this home is conveniently located near local amenities, schools, and parks, adding to the overall appeal of the property. Don't miss the chance to make 3125 Croton Ave your home sweet home!
